                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        f. 133ra: ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ጸሐፊሁ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ፲ወ፪ተፈጸመ፡ አመ፡ ፪፡ ለኅዳር፨ ለዓ፨ ዓለ፨ አ፨f. 133ra: May his prayer and grace be with the scribe Kidāna Māryām. (The book of) the 12 anaphoras has been completed on 2 Ḫǝdar. For eternity, amen.
                        Several letters were added in crude handwriting above the bottom line of the colophon, the letters are no longer legible.
                     </colophon>
