                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote type="rubrication" xml:id="d0">Nomina sacra; names of the ruling king, patriarch and metropolitan; names of the donors in supplication formulas; incipits of the texts; directives for the ministers; abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
